snippet.textDisplay:
I always figured it was about suicide although you could understand so many phrases of the lyrics as a depiction of a love relationship that ended. I don't know why i always figured since the lyrics "i hate you but i was just kidding myself" could really make you think of the contrary of hate which is love. But of course love is universal, it is everywhere in each and every relationship. Also, i guessed once it was about just about a "normal" death of someone. And all those three options they actually alluded to in the video. The relationship, the sick father and the suicide. Although the video is telling us the story of how it is supposed to be interpreted, we as listeners can put that song in our own context. And that Lewis, is something a great song does. It does tell a story but it leaves you room to feel free and interpret for youself. Get the strength out of it.
Well done!! I love it. And i hope you all are doing alright, love u Lewis stay the way you are and thank yoz for this masterpiece ❤
